<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Payment Successful</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #2196F3;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .payment-details {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border-left: 4px solid #2196F3;
    }
    .payment-details p {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .success-badge {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    strong {
      color: #2196F3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>✅ Payment Successful!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear Customer,</p>
    
    <div class="success-badge">
      Your payment has been successfully processed
    </div>
    
    <p>Thank you for completing your payment. Your order is now being processed and will be shipped soon.</p>
    
    <div class="payment-details">
      <h3>Payment Details</h3>
      <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> {{orderId}}</p>
      <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> ₹{{total}}</p>
      <p><strong>Payment Date:</strong> {{paymentDate}}</p>
      <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #4CAF50;">PAID</span></p>
    </div>
    
    <p>You can download your invoice from your account dashboard.</p>
    <p>We will notify you once your order has been shipped.</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for choosing <strong>RoboHatch</strong>!</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>RoboHatch - 3D Printing Made Easy</p>
    <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply to this message.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
